Package highscore

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HighScoreDatabase
    The HighScoreDatabase is the class that's mainly responsible for sorting the lists of usernames and scores for the HighScoreView class to display
    HighscoreDatabaseTest  
    HighScoreManager
    The HighScoreManager class parses a list of Accounts given to it and uses the methods in HighScoreDatabase to get to what is to be displayed on the the HighScoreView.
    Players
    This Players class stores two Lists containing the names of the players that have a high score and their respective score.
